Create manifest file
by: Brent Holden <bholden@redhat.com>


Description:
	The purpose of this script is to create a manifest programmatically using the local RPM database that you can feed into create-release
	


For help, simply run ./create-manifest --help

In addition to the script, you should find in this directory:
README  - This file


Changelog:

2/20/09 - 1.0
- Initial release
	* Support reading RPM db locally and creating manifest file based on installed packages
